title: Navigating the Common Challenges of Marriage, Part 4
itunes:author: John Fuller & Greg Smalley
itunes:summary: No matter what kind of marriage you have, bringing kids into the picture will always change things. Greg and John give you an idea of how to prepare. Featuring Dr. Gary Chapman.
